Red Games Co. Privacy Policy
Crayola Scribble Scrubbie Pets
Updated 1/29/2025
Crayola Scribble Scrubbie Pets (also known as Crayola Washimals) is operated by Red Games Co. on behalf of Crayola. As a globally recognized family-friendly brand, privacy and digital safety are top priorities for Crayola. To support this effort, we’ve provided this privacy statement to explain how we collect, use, and disclose personal information in clear, easy-to-understand language. This Privacy Policy may be updated at any time as new features are added or as the law changes. Please make sure you read everything here carefully, and if you happen to be a youngster (under 18 years old), ask an adult to help explain anything you don't understand.
